For Sqlite version
this is similar to:
/Users/yiguanghu/ccim/hisstory/rawdata/README

1.Install sqlite3
	/usr/bin/sqlite3
2. Download Sqlite driver from http://www.zentus.com/sqlitejdbc/
	put it under ~/.groovy/lib
3. run groovy ExtractVerseforaffirmation_sqlite.groovy

this generate db/renewal.db
groovy ConvertBibletxtto_sqlite.groovy
cp db/renewal.db /Users/yiguanghu/Documents/Titanium Studio Workspace/facetoface/Resources/
